‡§†‡•Ä‡§ï ‡§Ü‡§π‡•á! ‡§Ü‡§§‡§æ Get Payment by Booking ID component ‡§¨‡§®‡§µ‡•Ç. ‡§™‡•Ç‡§∞‡•ç‡§£ Angular standalone component + HTML + CSS style.


